'''Soylent'''是一种[[代餐|代餐]]饮料，被宣传为“主食餐”，有液体和粉末两种形式。其发明人声称Soylent能够满足一般成年人所有的[[参考膳食摄入量|营养需求]]，<ref name="Scutti"/>但批评家持有[[#健康影响|不同意见]]。Soylent最初是由软件工程师Rob Rhinehart作为自己对营养学的实验创造出来并加以测试。后来，粉末版Soylent被开发成了Soylent的第一条产品线，後來也開發了飲品版和Soylent Squared等零食。

Soylent声称当前配方是基于{{tsl|en|National Academy of Medicine|医学国家科学院}}<ref>[http://faq.soylent.com/hc/en-us/articles/200789315-Nutrition Nutrition - Soylent] {{Wayback|url=http://faq.soylent.com/hc/en-us/articles/200789315-Nutrition |date=20160310185540 }}. Retrieved 10 June 2015.</ref>的推荐，并符合当前[[美国食品药品监督管理局|食品药品监督管理局]]对食品的要求。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2014/01/soylent-gets-tested-scores-a-surprisingly-wholesome-nutritional-label/|title=Soylent gets tested, scores a surprisingly wholesome nutritional label|first=Lee|last=Hutchinson|work=Ars Technica|date=2014-01-29|accessdate=2015-06-11|quote=However, the results of the nutrition testing done to gain the label have established that Soylent meets the Food and Drug Administration's standards for a whole raft of healthy claims: "Everything from reduced risk of heart disease and some cancers to absence of tooth decay," said Rhinehart. Based on the testing, he explained, Soylent can make many of the health and nutrient claims that the FDA tracks.|archive-date=2015-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150613024801/http://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2014/01/soylent-gets-tested-scores-a-surprisingly-wholesome-nutritional-label/|dead-url=no}}</ref>Rosa Labs也声称Soylent包含健康食谱的所有元素，且不含过量的糖、饱和脂肪或胆固醇。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://faq.soylent.com/hc/en-us/articles/200836809-What-is-Soylent-|title=What is Soylent?|work=Soylent|accessdate=2016-05-21|archive-date=2016-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310185220/https://faq.soylent.com/hc/en-us/articles/200836809-What-is-Soylent-|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

== 历史 ==
=== 起源 ===
2013年1月，Rhunehart從[[生物化學|生物化學]]的課本及美國政府的網站中找到有關資訊，列出包括包括[[葡萄糖酸鉀|葡萄糖酸鉀]]、[[碳酸鈣|碳酸鈣]]、[[麥芽糊精|麥芽糊精]]等35種他認爲生存必須的化學材料<ref>{{Cite web|title=The End of Food|url=https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2014/05/12/the-end-of-food|accessdate=2020-06-22|last=Widdicombe|first=Lizzie|work=The New Yorker|language=en-us|archive-date=2020-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200724075842/https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2014/05/12/the-end-of-food|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他進行自我實驗，將購買回來的35種原料與水攪拌均勻後當作食物飲用三十天，結果發現這種的飲食方式不但節省金錢和時間，也改善了健康。在2013年2月13日，他在其部落格上发表了他的实验<ref>[http://robrhinehart.com/?p=298 How I Stopped Eating Food] {{Wayback|url=http://robrhinehart.com/?p=298 |date=20160514123511 }}. Feb 13, 2013. Retrieved April 4, 2015</ref>，并在稍后将营养信息和最初配方<ref>[http://robrhinehart.com/?p=424 What's in Soylent] {{Wayback|url=http://robrhinehart.com/?p=424 |date=20150330072737 }} Feb 14, 2013. Retrieved April 4, 2015</ref>共享给了有兴趣的人。
=== 商業發展 ===
Rhinehart在博客的分享引发了一场在{{tsl|en|Tilt.com|Tilt}}上筹得超过3百万美元<ref name="Scutti"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://crowdtilt.soylent.me/soylent-free-your-body|website=Tilt.com|title=Soylent - Free Your Body|publisher=Tilt.com|accessdate=2015-06-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141012152640/https://crowdtilt.soylent.me/soylent-free-your-body|archivedate=2014-10-12}}</ref>的[[众筹|众筹]]活动，该次活动的目标是将粉末饮品从概念推向生产。在活动之后，Soylent在种子轮得到了1.5百万美元<ref>[http://www.crowdfundinsider.com/2013/10/24870-crowdfunding-darling-soylent-nets-1-5-million-vc-funding/ Crowdfunding Darling Soylent Nets $1.5 Million In VC Funding] {{Wayback|url=http://www.crowdfundinsider.com/2013/10/24870-crowdfunding-darling-soylent-nets-1-5-million-vc-funding/ |date=20160415092417 }}. October 22, 2013</ref>的{{tsl|en|Venture capital financing|风险资本融资}}，用于进一步开发[[概念验证|概念验证]]。媒体报道了Rosa Labs在2014年4月开始生产，使用了500美元的小型系统发送了头2.6百万美元的产品。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://medium.com/@alando46/how-we-spent-500-on-tech-to-ship-2-6m-of-soylent-3abfdcebee78|title=How We Spent $500 on Tech to Ship $2.6M of Soylent|author=Alando Ballantyne|work=Medium|accessdate=2016-05-21|archive-date=2016-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306092655/https://medium.com/@alando46/how-we-spent-500-on-tech-to-ship-2-6m-of-soylent-3abfdcebee78|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2015年1月，Soylent收到了由天使投资人[[Andreessen_Horowitz|Andreessen Horowitz]]带头的20百万美元{{tsl|en|Series A round|A轮投资}}。<ref>[http://robrhinehart.com/?p=1192 Soylent Raises Money] {{Wayback|url=http://robrhinehart.com/?p=1192 |date=20150121163816 }}. Retrieved 22 January 2015.</ref>

2015年6月15日，Soylent進入[[加拿大|加拿大]]市場，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blog.soylent.com/post/121573571522/now-shipping-to-canada|title=Soylent : Now Shipping to Canada|work=soylent.com|access-date=2016-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618014259/http://blog.soylent.com/post/121573571522/now-shipping-to-canada|archive-date=2015-06-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>但在2017年因加拿大對代餐的法律規定開始停售，直至2020年4月重新上架。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Meal Replacement Startup Soylent Returns To Canada For First Time Since 2017|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/christinatroitino/2020/04/13/meal-replacement-startup-soylent-returns-to-canada-for-first-time-since-2017/|accessdate=2020-06-22|last=Troitino|first=Christina|work=Forbes|language=en|archive-date=2020-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200625142409/https://www.forbes.com/sites/christinatroitino/2020/04/13/meal-replacement-startup-soylent-returns-to-canada-for-first-time-since-2017/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在2015年7月，Soylent会将其公司总部搬到位于[[洛杉矶市中心|洛杉矶市中心]]的百乐汇媒体中心。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.us.jll.com/united-states/en-us/news/3522/soylent-to-relocate-headquarters-to-broadway-media-center-in-downtown-los-angeles|title=Soylent To Relocate Headquarters to Broadway Media Center in Downtown Los Angeles|work=JLL|access-date=2016-05-21|archive-date=2018-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181007174917/http://www.us.jll.com/united-states/en-us/news/3522/soylent-to-relocate-headquarters-to-broadway-media-center-in-downtown-los-angeles}}</ref>

2018年9月，Soylent在[[英國|英國]]開始發售。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Soylent is coming to the UK to put an end to your chewing woes|url=https://www.wired.co.uk/article/soylent-uk-launch-meal-replacement-drink|last=Leprince-Ringuet|first=Daphne|date=2018-09-18|journal=Wired UK|issn=1357-0978|access-date=2020-06-22|archive-date=2020-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200625110101/https://www.wired.co.uk/article/soylent-uk-launch-meal-replacement-drink|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 产品历史 ===

在2014年5月的第一周，Soylent 1.0的第一批美国订单开始出货。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://discourse.soylent.me/t/soylent-update-5-1/12590 |title=Soylent Update |publisher=Discourse.soylent.me |date=2014-05-01 |accessdate=2014-05-06 |archive-date=2014-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140506005255/http://discourse.soylent.me/t/soylent-update-5-1/12590 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在此之后产品有数次更改，每次都有不同的“版本”。自2014年11月的Soylent 1.2之后，所有版本都是素食的。<ref name="Announcing Soylent 1.2">{{cite web|url=http://blog.soylent.me/post/102285900727/announcing-soylent-1-2-development-of-the-soylent|title=Soylent : Announcing Soylent 1.2  Development of the Soylent...|work=soylent.me|access-date=2016-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141205114847/http://blog.soylent.me/post/102285900727/announcing-soylent-1-2-development-of-the-soylent|archive-date=2014-12-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>在2015年2月推出的1.4版考虑到来自[[哥伦比亚大学|哥伦比亚大学]]的药学教授F. Xavier Pi-Sunyer的建议，使用了43/40/17的碳水化合物/脂肪/蛋白质比例。<ref>[http://discourse.soylent.me/t/nutrition-advisor-for-soylent/19994 Nutrition advisor for Soylent] {{Wayback|url=http://discourse.soylent.me/t/nutrition-advisor-for-soylent/19994 |date=20150403150618 }}. 16 March 2015.</ref>在2015年6月推出的1.5版更将此比例调整到了45/40/15，<ref name="soylent-blog-1.5">{{cite web|url=http://blog.soylent.com/post/120465411252/soylent-1-5-has-arrived|title=Soylent : Soylent 1.5 Has Arrived|work=soylent.com|access-date=2016-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150602085014/http://blog.soylent.com/post/120465411252/soylent-1-5-has-arrived|archive-date=2015-06-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>并有65的[[升糖指数|升糖指数]]和35的[[升糖负荷|升糖负荷]]。<ref name="soylent glycemic">{{cite web|url=http://faq.soylent.com/hc/en-us/articles/204819889|title=Soylent Glycemic Data|work=Soylent|accessdate=2016-05-21|archive-date=2016-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306021928/https://faq.soylent.com/hc/en-us/articles/204819889|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

在2015年8月3日，公司宣布了“Soylent 2.0”，是该司的第一种可直接饮用的Soylent产品。此预先混合的产品每瓶为400卡路里，并在2015年9月9日首次亮相。<ref name="arstechnica.com-soylent-2.0-premixed">{{cite web|url=http://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2015/08/soylent-2-0-is-coming-pre-mixed-in-a-bottle/|title=Soylent 2.0 is coming—pre-mixed, in a bottle|work=Ars Technica|accessdate=2016-05-21|archive-date=2015-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150805145122/http://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2015/08/soylent-2-0-is-coming-pre-mixed-in-a-bottle/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

