== 口味 ==

Soylent包含用于{{tsl|en|Flavor masker|掩盖口味}}及调整外观、材质和气味的[[大豆|大豆]][[卵磷脂|卵磷脂]]和[[三氯蔗糖|三氯蔗糖]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=There is more to food than nutrition|url=http://blog.soylent.me/post/73232819517/there-is-more-to-food-than-nutrition-even-a|accessdate=2014-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140913172541/http://blog.soylent.me/post/73232819517/there-is-more-to-food-than-nutrition-even-a|archive-date=2014-09-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>Rhinehart称Soylent的口味为“极简”、“宽广”和“不特定”的。<ref>{{citation |url=http://www.inc.com/amy-whyte/stephen-colbert-tries-liquid-food-substitute-soylent.html |title=Stephen Colbert Taste Tests Soylent... And Finds It Delicious? |work=[[Inc._(magazine)|Inc. (magazine)]] |date=2014-06-13 |quote=Rhinehart described the "minimal flavor" as "broad" and "nonspecific" |accessdate=2016-05-21 |archive-date=2016-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414175056/http://www.inc.com/amy-whyte/stephen-colbert-tries-liquid-food-substitute-soylent.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>1.4版之前的Soylent还包含了用于调味的配料[[香兰素|香兰素]]。<ref>{{citation |url=http://blog.soylent.me/post/112067551237/soylent-1-4-begins-shipping-today |title=Soylent 1.4 begins shipping today. |accessdate=2015-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150227041706/http://blog.soylent.me/post/112067551237/soylent-1-4-begins-shipping-today |archive-date=2015-02-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

对粉状Soylent的口味评论褒贬不一。赞扬者们为其“浓厚、柔滑、诡异地令人满足”的口味“高兴地惊讶”，<ref name=verge>{{citation |url=http://www.theverge.com/2014/7/17/5893221/soylent-survivor-one-month-living-on-lab-made-liquid-nourishment |title=Soylent survivor: one month living on lab-made liquid nourishment |work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]] |date=2014-07-17 |accessdate=2016-05-21 |archive-date=2016-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160518083830/http://www.theverge.com/2014/7/17/5893221/soylent-survivor-one-month-living-on-lab-made-liquid-nourishment |dead-url=no }}</ref>或者认为其口味类似香草奶昔而口感类似面糊。<ref>{{citation|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/soylent-review-2014-7|title=Soylent Review|work=[[Business_Insider|Business Insider]]|date=2014-07-14|accessdate=2016-05-21|archive-date=2016-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160523080406/http://www.businessinsider.com/soylent-review-2014-7|dead-url=no}}</ref>负面评论则称其“无聊得折磨人”、“如抹布拧出来的水”、<ref>{{citation |url=http://gawker.com/we-drank-soylent-the-weird-food-of-the-future-510293401 |title=We Drank Soylent The Weird Food of the Future |work=[[Gawker|Gawker]] |date=2013-05-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141005014300/http://gawker.com/we-drank-soylent-the-weird-food-of-the-future-510293401 |archivedate=2014-10-05 |accessdate=2016-05-21 }}</ref>“故意显得平淡”、恶劣得使品尝者“作呕”，<ref>{{citation|url=http://www.theguardian.com/global/2016/feb/08/inside-stupid-hackathon-extremely-stupid-ideas|title=Mansplain it to Me: inside the Stupid Hackathon for extremely stupid ideas|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|date=2016-02-08|accessdate=2016-02-08|archive-date=2016-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160208185053/http://www.theguardian.com/global/2016/feb/08/inside-stupid-hackathon-extremely-stupid-ideas|dead-url=no}}</ref>或者是尝起来类似“自制无毒[[培乐多|培乐多]]”。<ref name=verge/><ref>{{citation |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/05/29/technology/personaltech/the-soylent-revolution-will-not-be-pleasurable.html |title=The Soylent Revolution Will Not Be Pleasurable |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=2014-05-28 |last=Manjoo |first=Farhad |accessdate=2016-05-21 |archive-date=2016-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160518173711/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/05/29/technology/personaltech/the-soylent-revolution-will-not-be-pleasurable.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>也有人将其与{{tsl|en|Slim Fast}}对比。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2016/apr/01/food-technology-soylent-slimfast-juice-fasting|title=Food tech is just men rebranding what women have done for decades|author=Nellie Bowles|work=the Guardian|accessdate=2016-05-21|archive-date=2016-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424232041/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2016/apr/01/food-technology-soylent-slimfast-juice-fasting|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 健康影响 ==

Soylent的生产者声称其包含健康生活方式所必须的所有营养需求，而此声称已经被独立地测试并证实。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Hutchinson|first1=Lee|title=Soylent gets tested, scores a surprisingly wholesome nutritional label|url=http://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2014/01/soylent-gets-tested-scores-a-surprisingly-wholesome-nutritional-label/|website=Ars Technica|accessdate=2016-02-23|date=2014-01-29|archive-date=2015-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150613024801/http://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2014/01/soylent-gets-tested-scores-a-surprisingly-wholesome-nutritional-label/|dead-url=no}}</ref>仅依赖Soylent为生可能会带来社会性的负面影响。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Ziegler|first1=Chris|title=Soylent survivor: one month living on lab-made liquid nourishment|url=http://www.theverge.com/2014/7/17/5893221/soylent-survivor-one-month-living-on-lab-made-liquid-nourishment|website=The Verge|accessdate=2016-02-23|date=2014-07-17|archive-date=2016-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160220042343/http://www.theverge.com/2014/7/17/5893221/soylent-survivor-one-month-living-on-lab-made-liquid-nourishment|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 获提出的65号提案诉讼 ==

在2015年8月13日，非盈利的环保和企业社会责任监督{{tsl|en|As You Sow}}提交了一份意图向Soylent的生产者发起诉讼的意向通知，声称Soylent未有妥善地标注出其产品中的铅及镉含量。该诉讼基于加利福尼亚州的{{tsl|en|California Proposition 65 (1986)|65号提案}}作出，该法对包含痕量特定物质的食品要求额外的标签。尽管Soylent中的铅和镉含量远低于FDA所设定的国家级安全水平，其[[铅|铅]]含量确实高于65号提案所允许的含量12至25倍，而[[镉|镉]]则为4倍。<ref name=eater/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/as-you-sow-files-notice-of-legal-action-against-soylent-super-food-300128427.html|website=PR News Wire|date=2015-08-13|title=As You Sow Files Notice Of Legal Action Against Soylent Super Food|access-date=2016-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160512045854/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/as-you-sow-files-notice-of-legal-action-against-soylent-super-food-300128427.html|archive-date=2016-05-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>曾进行过65号提案相关的和解工作的一名律师将该案描述为“危言耸听”，因这些水平远低于FDA限制。<ref name=foodnav/>Soylent的网站目前展示了必要的65号提案警告。<ref name=foodnav>{{cite web|url=http://www.foodnavigator-usa.com/Manufacturers/Soylent-hits-back-at-legal-threat-We-display-Prop-65-warnings|title=Soylent case reignites debate over Prop 65: 'It's basically extortion,' claims attorney|first=Elaine|last=Watson|date=2015-08-17|accessdate=2016-05-21|archive-date=2015-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150816004850/http://www.foodnavigator-usa.com/Manufacturers/Soylent-hits-back-at-legal-threat-We-display-Prop-65-warnings|dead-url=no}}</ref>As You Sow提出，因为Soylent称自己为其他餐食的完全替代品，这些含量即可能有害。<ref name=eater>{{cite web|url=http://www.eater.com/2015/8/16/9162301/soylent-as-you-sow-cadmium-lead-california|title=Soylent Under Fire For Allegedly Failing to Provide Adequate Warnings On Its Labels|first=Brenna|last=Houck|work=Eater|date=2015-08-16|accessdate=2015-08-16|archive-date=2015-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150817124808/http://www.eater.com/2015/8/16/9162301/soylent-as-you-sow-cadmium-lead-california|dead-url=no}}</ref>该要求是基于对生殖毒性的允许水平提出的，这种水平远低于对毒性或[[致癌性|致癌性]]的允许水平。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2015/08/watchdog-group-says-soylents-cadmium-and-lead-levels-violate-ca-law/|title=Watchdog group says Soylent's cadmium and lead levels violate CA law|first=Lee|last=Hutchinson|work=Ars Technica|date=2015-08-17|accessdate=2015-08-17|archive-date=2015-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150819043415/http://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2015/08/watchdog-group-says-soylents-cadmium-and-lead-levels-violate-ca-law/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

